name: Spartan
short_description: Sparta token (300) is a novelty project, it aims to be a store of value with a supply of only 300.
description: With Spartan, everyone will be able to get unique and limited NFTs to gain access to certain chats and also earn our In game currency, Iron Bars. We have recreated the ancient Spartan civilization on our Didcord server, that is where The City of Sparta was born for us, there you will get your Role and access to new private rooms only for those who really deserve to be part of Sparta..
